redictive options based on user’s input or context,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","abstract":[{"text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" extensions and ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewModifiers","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","title":"Components","images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"}]}}}